## 2) `.gitignore`

This will keep your venv, Python cache, and editor junk out of Git.

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.env
*.venv
.env
.venv/
ENV/
env/
venv/

# VS Code / editors
.vscode/
.idea/

# Byte-compiled / packaging
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/

# Mac / OS
.DS_Store

# pytest / coverage (if added later)
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/

# Flask instance folder (if you ever add it)
instance/
